{
  "title":       "Tinted Images",
  "url":         "/blog/tinted-images/",
  "permalink":   "http://localhost:42421/blog/tinted-images/",
  "date":        "2025-01-10",
  "tags":        ["palette","images"],
  "summary":     "Monochrome images tinted to any base16 colour with CSS mask-image.",
  "readingTime": 1,
  "content":     "\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ccode\u003etinted-image\u003c/code\u003e shortcode recolours monochrome images (SVG, PNG) to\nany palette slot using CSS \u003ccode\u003emask-image\u003c/code\u003e. No JavaScript, no\napproximation — the colour is an exact CSS custom property.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"single-colour\"\u003eSingle colour\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n     role=\"img\"\n     aria-label=\"Terminal\"\n     style=\"\n       background-color: var(--base0D);\n       -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n       mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n       width: 64px;\n       height: 64px;\n     \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"chroma\"\u003e\u003ccode class=\"language-go-html-template\" data-lang=\"go-html-template\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cp\"\u003e{{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"err\"\u003e\u0026lt;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003etinted\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"err\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eimage\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003esrc\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;/images/terminal.svg\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ecolor\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;base0D\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ewidth\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;64px\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eheight\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;64px\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"err\"\u003e\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cp\"\u003e}}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"palette-sampler\"\u003ePalette sampler\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe same image in every accent colour:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:1rem; align-items:center; margin:1rem 0;\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Red\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base08);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Orange\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base09);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Yellow\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0A);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Green\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0B);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Cyan\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0C);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Blue\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0D);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Purple\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0E);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Brown\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0F);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"different-shapes\"\u003eDifferent shapes\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAny monochrome image works — opaque pixels become the tinted colour,\ntransparent pixels stay transparent.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:1.5rem; align-items:center; margin:1rem 0;\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Code\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0B);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/code.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/code.svg');\n         width: 56px;\n         height: 56px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Gear\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base09);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/gear.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/gear.svg');\n         width: 56px;\n         height: 56px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Globe\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0C);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/globe.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/globe.svg');\n         width: 56px;\n         height: 56px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Heart\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base08);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/heart.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/heart.svg');\n         width: 56px;\n         height: 56px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-it-works\"\u003eHow it works\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe image acts as an alpha mask on a coloured \u003ccode\u003e\u0026lt;div\u0026gt;\u003c/code\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"chroma\"\u003e\u003ccode class=\"language-css\" data-lang=\"css\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nc\"\u003etinted-image\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003ebackground-color\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nf\"\u003evar\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e--\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003ebase0D\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e);\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003emask-image\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003eurl\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u0026#39;/images/logo.svg\u0026#39;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e);\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003emask-size\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"kc\"\u003econtain\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003emask-repeat\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"kc\"\u003eno-repeat\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eOpaque pixels → colour shows. Transparent pixels → nothing renders.\nSwap the palette and every tinted image updates instantly.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"parameters\"\u003eParameters\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdl class=\"info-list\"\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003e\u003ccode\u003esrc\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003ePath to a monochrome image (required)\u003c/dd\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003e\u003ccode\u003ecolor\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eBase16 slot name, e.g. \u003ccode\u003ebase0D\u003c/code\u003e (default: \u003ccode\u003ebase0D\u003c/code\u003e)\u003c/dd\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003e\u003ccode\u003ealt\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eAccessible label\u003c/dd\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003e\u003ccode\u003ewidth\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eCSS width (default: \u003ccode\u003eauto\u003c/code\u003e)\u003c/dd\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003e\u003ccode\u003eheight\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eCSS height (default: \u003ccode\u003eauto\u003c/code\u003e)\u003c/dd\u003e\n\u003c/dl\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBest results with images that are solid white (or any opaque colour) on\na transparent background. SVGs work perfectly; PNGs need an alpha channel.\u003c/p\u003e\n"
},
{
  "title":       "Theme",
  "url":         "/blog/theme/",
  "permalink":   "http://localhost:42421/blog/theme/",
  "date":        "2025-01-05",
  "tags":        ["palette","typography"],
  "summary":     "Palette and typography flow from a single data file.",
  "readingTime": 1,
  "content":     "\u003cp\u003eEvery colour on this site comes from the sixteen CSS custom properties\nemitted by \u003ccode\u003edata/colorscheme.yaml\u003c/code\u003e. Swap the YAML, rebuild, done.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"preview-a-different-palette\"\u003ePreview a different palette\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePick a scheme and watch the whole page re-tint in place. Reload to\nrestore the built-in palette.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"theme-selector\"\u003e\n  \u003clabel class=\"theme-selector__label\" for=\"theme-selector\"\u003epreview palette:\u003c/label\u003e\n  \u003cselect id=\"theme-selector\" class=\"theme-selector__input\"\u003e\n    \u003coption value=\"\"\u003eKanagawa (current)\u003c/option\u003e\n    \u003coption value=\"tokyo-night-storm\"\u003eTokyo Night Storm\u003c/option\u003e\n    \u003coption value=\"gruvbox-dark\"\u003eGruvbox Dark\u003c/option\u003e\n    \u003coption value=\"nord\"\u003eNord\u003c/option\u003e\n    \u003coption value=\"catppuccin-mocha\"\u003eCatppuccin Mocha\u003c/option\u003e\n    \u003coption value=\"solarized-dark\"\u003eSolarized Dark\u003c/option\u003e\n    \u003coption value=\"github-light\"\u003eGitHub Light\u003c/option\u003e\n  \u003c/select\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cscript type=\"module\"\u003e\nconst schemes = {\n  '': {\n    base00:'1F1F28',base01:'16161D',base02:'223249',base03:'54546D',\n    base04:'727169',base05:'DCD7BA',base06:'C8C093',base07:'717C7C',\n    base08:'C34043',base09:'FFA066',base0A:'C0A36E',base0B:'76946A',\n    base0C:'6A9589',base0D:'7E9CD8',base0E:'957FB8',base0F:'D27E99',\n  },\n  'tokyo-night-storm': {\n    base00:'24283b',base01:'1f2335',base02:'292e42',base03:'565f89',\n    base04:'545c7e',base05:'a9b1d6',base06:'c0caf5',base07:'394b70',\n    base08:'f7768e',base09:'ff9e64',base0A:'e0af68',base0B:'9ece6a',\n    base0C:'89ddff',base0D:'7aa2f7',base0E:'bb9af7',base0F:'c0caf5',\n  },\n  'gruvbox-dark': {\n    base00:'282828',base01:'3c3836',base02:'504945',base03:'665c54',\n    base04:'bdae93',base05:'d5c4a1',base06:'ebdbb2',base07:'fbf1c7',\n    base08:'fb4934',base09:'fe8019',base0A:'fabd2f',base0B:'b8bb26',\n    base0C:'8ec07c',base0D:'83a598',base0E:'d3869b',base0F:'d65d0e',\n  },\n  'nord': {\n    base00:'2e3440',base01:'3b4252',base02:'434c5e',base03:'4c566a',\n    base04:'d8dee9',base05:'e5e9f0',base06:'eceff4',base07:'8fbcbb',\n    base08:'bf616a',base09:'d08770',base0A:'ebcb8b',base0B:'a3be8c',\n    base0C:'88c0d0',base0D:'81a1c1',base0E:'b48ead',base0F:'5e81ac',\n  },\n  'catppuccin-mocha': {\n    base00:'1e1e2e',base01:'181825',base02:'313244',base03:'45475a',\n    base04:'585b70',base05:'cdd6f4',base06:'f5e0dc',base07:'b4befe',\n    base08:'f38ba8',base09:'fab387',base0A:'f9e2af',base0B:'a6e3a1',\n    base0C:'94e2d5',base0D:'89b4fa',base0E:'cba6f7',base0F:'f2cdcd',\n  },\n  'solarized-dark': {\n    base00:'002b36',base01:'073642',base02:'586e75',base03:'657b83',\n    base04:'839496',base05:'93a1a1',base06:'eee8d5',base07:'fdf6e3',\n    base08:'dc322f',base09:'cb4b16',base0A:'b58900',base0B:'859900',\n    base0C:'2aa198',base0D:'268bd2',base0E:'6c71c4',base0F:'d33682',\n  },\n  'github-light': {\n    base00:'ffffff',base01:'f6f8fa',base02:'d0d7de',base03:'8c959f',\n    base04:'6e7781',base05:'24292f',base06:'1f2328',base07:'0550ae',\n    base08:'cf222e',base09:'fb8500',base0A:'9a6700',base0B:'116329',\n    base0C:'1f6feb',base0D:'0969da',base0E:'8250df',base0F:'a40e26',\n  },\n};\nconst sel = document.getElementById('theme-selector');\nsel.addEventListener('change', () =\u003e {\n  const scheme = schemes[sel.value];\n  if (!scheme) return;\n  const root = document.documentElement;\n  for (const [k, v] of Object.entries(scheme)) {\n    root.style.setProperty(`--${k}`, `#${v}`);\n  }\n});\n\u003c/script\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"current-palette\"\u003eCurrent palette\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"palette\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base00\" style=\"background-color: var(--base00);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase00\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base01\" style=\"background-color: var(--base01);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase01\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base02\" style=\"background-color: var(--base02);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase02\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base03\" style=\"background-color: var(--base03);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase03\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base04\" style=\"background-color: var(--base04);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase04\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base05\" style=\"background-color: var(--base05);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase05\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base06\" style=\"background-color: var(--base06);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase06\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base07\" style=\"background-color: var(--base07);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase07\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base08\" style=\"background-color: var(--base08);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase08\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base09\" style=\"background-color: var(--base09);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase09\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base0A\" style=\"background-color: var(--base0A);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase0A\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base0B\" style=\"background-color: var(--base0B);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase0B\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base0C\" style=\"background-color: var(--base0C);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase0C\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base0D\" style=\"background-color: var(--base0D);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase0D\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base0E\" style=\"background-color: var(--base0E);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase0E\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"palette__swatch\" data-slot=\"base0F\" style=\"background-color: var(--base0F);\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"palette__label\"\u003ebase0F\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cscript type=\"module\"\u003e\n\ndocument.querySelectorAll('.palette__swatch').forEach((el) =\u003e {\n  const slot = el.getAttribute('data-slot');\n  const val = getComputedStyle(document.documentElement)\n    .getPropertyValue(`--${slot}`)\n    .trim();\n  el.title = `${slot}: ${val}`;\n});\n\u003c/script\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo ship your own palette, drop a \u003ccode\u003edata/colorscheme.yaml\u003c/code\u003e in your site\nroot:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"chroma\"\u003e\u003ccode class=\"language-yaml\" data-lang=\"yaml\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003ename\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"l\"\u003eMy Palette\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003escheme\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e  \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003ebase00\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s2\"\u003e\u0026#34;1F1F28\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e  \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e# …\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e  \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003ebase0F\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s2\"\u003e\u0026#34;D27E99\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eHex values without a leading \u003ccode\u003e#\u003c/code\u003e (standard base16 format).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"typography\"\u003eTypography\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdl class=\"info-list\"\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003eFont family\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eFiraCode Nerd Font, ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace\u003c/dd\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003eBase size\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003e15px\u003c/dd\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003eLine height\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003e1.6\u003c/dd\u003e\n\u003c/dl\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTTF files ship in \u003ccode\u003estatic/fonts/\u003c/code\u003e, loaded with \u003ccode\u003efont-display: swap\u003c/code\u003e.\nFiraCode ligatures render in code blocks, and the Nerd Font patches\nprovide the \u003ca href=\"/blog/icons/\"\u003eicon\u003c/a\u003e\n glyphs used throughout the UI.\u003c/p\u003e\n"
